text.tspan: The weak form of the Helmholtz equation

g.ns0:text:
\begin{lstlisting}[language=python] 
f = state.scalar_fields["Tracer"]

v = TestFunction(f)
u = TrialFunction(f)

lmbda = 1
A = (dot(grad(v), grad(u)) - lmbda*v*u) * dx

RHS = v * f * dx

solve(A == RHS, f)
\end{lstlisting}
